import React from 'react'; import { Process } from '../utils/types'; interface ResultTableProps { processes: Process[]; averageWaitingTime: number; averageTurnaroundTime: number; averageResponseTime: number; } const ResultTable: React.FC = ({ processes, averageWaitingTime, averageTurnaroundTime, averageResponseTime }) => { return (
{processes.map((process) => ( ))}
Process ID Arrival Time Burst Time Completion Time Turnaround Time Waiting Time Response Time
{process.id} {process.arrivalTime} {process.burstTime} {process.completionTime} {process.turnaroundTime} {process.waitingTime} {process.responseTime}
Average Waiting Time: {averageWaitingTime.toFixed(2)}
Average Turnaround Time: {averageTurnaroundTime.toFixed(2)}
Average Response Time: {averageResponseTime.toFixed(2)}
); }; export default ResultTable;
